 of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Chaworth was born about 1148, in Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Alice Alfeton."},"et":{"Abt 1148–":"umbes 1148–Surnud","1151–Female":"1151–Surnud","1164–1246":"1164–1246","1179–Male":"1179–Surnud","1148–Male":"1148–Surnud","1148":"1148","1246":"1246","1179":"1179","1164":"1164","Abt 1148":"umbes 1148","1151":"1151","about 1164":"umbes 1164","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","of,Chaworth,Nottinghamshire,England":"Nottinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1148–":"noin 1148–Kuollut","1151–Female":"1151–Kuollut","1164–1246":"1164–1246","1179–Male":"1179–Kuollut","1148–Male":"1148–Kuollut","1148":"1148","1246":"1246","1179":"1179","1164":"1164","Abt 1148":"noin 1148","1151":"1151","about 1164":"noin 1164","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","of,Chaworth,Nottinghamshire,England":"Nottinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1148–":"environ 1148–Décédé","1151–Female":"1151–Décédée","1164–1246":"1164–1246","1179–Male":"1179–Décédé","1148–Male":"1148–Décédé","1148":"1148","1246":"1246","1179":"1179","1164":"1164","Abt 1148":"environ 1148","1151":"1151","about 1164":"environ 1164","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre","of,Chaworth,Nottinghamshire,England":"Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William Chaworth est né environ 1148, à Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Alice Alfeton."},"de":{"Abt 1148–":"um 1148–Verstorben","1151–Female":"1151–Verstorben","1164–1246":"1164–1246","1179–Male":"1179–Verstorben","1148–Male":"1148–Verstorben","1148":"1148","1246":"1246","1179":"1179","1164":"1164","Abt 1148":"um 1148","1151":"1151","about 1164":"um 1164","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England